  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A first person shooter where players see who can survive to be the last one alive as the flood below them rises. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players are pitted against each other in a research lab with a helicopter pad on top in which players can go from one level to another leading to one fire fight to the next in this fast paced combat FPS Battle Royale. There can only be one survivor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additional Game Modes Present. </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A first person shooter where players see who can survive to be the last one alive as the flood below them rises. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players are pitted against each other in a research lab with a helicopter pad on top in which players can go from one level to another leading to one fire fight to the next in this fast paced combat FPS Battle Royale. There can only be one survivor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additional Game Modes Present. </p>",
